{"lemma":"عُرامُ","slug":"عُرامُ","root":"ع.ر.م","root_slug":"ع-ر-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28843"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28843","headword_ar":"عُرَامٌ","root":"Erm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [mentioned in the first sentence of this art. as an inf. n.,] (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) when used as [a simple subst.] denoting a quality of a boy, or child, (S, Mgh,) or of a man, (K,) signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Evilness of disposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"illnature, and exceeding perverseness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crossness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repugnance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, * TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharpness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"annoyance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"molestation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [and] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quality of quitting the right course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exorbitance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 277.) ―         -b2-  Hence, in a trad. of 'Omar, metaphorically used as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharpness and strength"},{"kind":"text","text":"of [the beverage termed]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy*","text_ar":"نَبِيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":"made of raisins. (Mgh.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Numerousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an army, (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharpness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof. (K.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ignorance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA.)       -A2-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraAq","text_ar":"عُرَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flesh-meat"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a bone: and likewise [i. e., app.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portions that are cropped"},{"kind":"text","text":"by camels] of trees. (S, K. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraAqN","text_ar":"عُرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaroqN","text_ar":"عَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoramu","text_ar":"اَعْرَمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalobK EalaY EuraAmK","text_ar":"كَلْبٍ عَلَى عُرَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More evil in disposition than a dog over a piece of flesh-meat of a bone"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) Or, accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuraAmu","text_ar":"العُرَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies, (TA,) or it signifies also, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What falls of the bark of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thorn-tree called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eawosaj","text_ar":"عَوْسَج"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) but others explain it in a general manner, saying that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraAmu","text_ar":"عُرَامُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ajarapi","text_ar":"الشَّجَرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bark of the tree."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaromN","text_ar":"عَرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}